.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">913b</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; also <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. ὑὸν ἀντὶ τῶν χρημάτων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg020:219d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ly.\">Ly.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">219d</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρὸ ἀρετῆς κάλλος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:727d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">727d</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πλέον αὑτῶν</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:777d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">777d</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βραχυλογίαν μᾶλλον ἢ μῆκος</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:887b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">887b</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n90524.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. only, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">prefer in honour</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">esteem</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταῦτα ἐγὼ π</foreign>. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Heraclit.</author> </bibl> l.c.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐ π. τι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:739\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a cla